}

docs {
  # Course Instructors

  Manages instructor assignments to course instances.

  ## Endpoints
  - POST   /api/v1/course-instructors                          — Assign instructor
  - GET    /api/v1/course-instances/:id/instructors            — List instructors
  - DELETE /api/v1/course-instructors/:instanceID/:userID      — Remove instructor

  ## Allowed Roles
  - Lead Instructor
  - Instructor
  - TA

  ## Variable Flow
  Assign Instructor → saves INSTRUCTOR_USER_ID
  Remove Instructor → uses COURSE_INSTANCE_ID + INSTRUCTOR_USER_ID
}
